mixin CardPool(title, percent, total, invested, claimable)
    article.card-pool&attributes(attributes)
        div.__row
            h4.__title= title
            p.__permonth
                span= percent 
                | % per month
        p.__info 
            | Total staked: 
            span= total
            br
            | Your invest: 
            span= invested
            br
            | Claimable:
            span= claimable
        div.__buttons
            +Button(
                "claimButton",
                "xs",
                "brand",
                "true"
            ) 
                | Claim
            +Button(
                "stakeButton",
                "xs",
                "brand",
                "true"
            ) 
                | Stake